<h1>Weather</h1><div><figure class="floatleft"><img src="articles/img/weatherPic.png" alt="weatherPic.png"><figcaption>Visual</figcaption></figure><p><em>Weather</em> is the compunent, which is required for setting up parameters for the air: temperature, heat capacity and density. To set up the temperature this component is combined with scheduler of any type. Heat capacity anddensity are defined by user as properties: <em>airDensity</em> (default 1.2250) and <em>c</em> (default value=1005.4).</p></div><figure><img src="articles/img/weatherProperties.png" alt="weatherProperties.png"><figcaption>Properties</figcaption></figure><figure><img src="articles/img/weatherWithScheduler.png" alt="weatherWithScheduler.png"><figcaption>Setting up <em>Weather</em> temperature by <em>Scheduler</em></figcaption></figure>